params.markdown:
Overview

This Dashboard gives a detailed view of a Logstash pipeline.
   
Use the filters to drill down on individual nodes and pipelines. This view works best when focused on a single pipeline.
  
Plugin drilldowns are available by clicking on the plugin in the table views for inputs, filters and outputs.    

Specialized drilldowns are available for the dissect and grok filters, and the elasticsearch output.
